description: The Spirit must uncover the secret of a devilish experiment conducted by a deranged psychologist named Reynard.
name: Fox at Bay

description: Utilizing heavy inks and distorted panels, Eisner tells the tale of Quadrant J. Stet, an accountant who finds himself going blind and needs an expensive operation to save his vision.
name: The Embezzler (a.k.a. Quadrant J. Stet)

description: In part one of a two-part tale continued in "Bring in Sand Saref," the Spirit reminisces about his childhood friend, the big love of his youth.
name: Sand Saref

description: Continuing from "Sand Saref," the Spirit searches for his lost love who has since become a international criminal.
name: Bring in Sand Saref

description: As the Justice League and the Justice Lords battle for the fate of both worlds, Lord Superman does the unthinkable.
name: Justice Lords Beyond: The Return of Wonder Woman, Part 7 of 8: Homecomings

description:
The Hulk clashes with the ruthless warlord Attuma miles below the ocean surface! More action from Mark Waid and Leinil Francis Yu!

The warrior woman Thundra arrives from the future to challenge the Hulk!

By Jeff Parker and Mitch Breitweiser.

The Red She-Hulk has turned savage! Can Machine Man stop her?!

By Jeff Parker, Carlo Pagulayan and Wellinton Alves.

Collects:

  • Indestructible Hulk #5.
  • Hulk: Raging Thunder #1.
  • Red She-Hulk #61.
